com.btilm305.clashapi

Interface ClashAPI


  • public interface ClashAPI
    An API that contains operations listed at https://developer.clashofclans.com/#/documentation

    To get an instance of ClashAPI, invoke BTClashWrapper.getAPIInstance(String apiToken) with your API token
